                            <comment id="81474" author="yong.fan" created="Sat, 12 Apr 2014 10:48:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is another failure instance of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4803&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite sanity-scrub, subtest test_12&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4803&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4803&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="81473" author="yong.fan" created="Sat, 12 Apr 2014 10:47:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is because we inject failure at the test beginning, which cause some OST-object will be destroyed unexpected. I will fix related bugs in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4803&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite sanity-scrub, subtest test_12&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4803&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4803&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="81472" author="adilger" created="Sat, 12 Apr 2014 04:41:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hit this on &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fb7c66b0-c08e-11e3-ae98-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fb7c66b0-c08e-11e3-ae98-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
